  "about_the_game": "<strong>Are they caterpillars? Are they worms? They’re SNIKS!</strong> Multicoloured little snakes, indulging in fruits. Some of them are into strawberries, others into pears and all the other good stuff. There’s only one problem: They keep getting in one another‘s way while eating. Your task: Untie the Gordian Knot of SNIKS and help them eat all the fruits.<br><br>SNIKS is something for your brain, making you puzzle your way through 110 handcrafted levels. SNIKS is also a feast for the eyes: Tasty fruits, hand-drawn environments and colorful sniks form a beautiful fruit salad. <br><br><strong>Start puzzling now!</strong><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258020/extras/5ee32287d6f8233060375820ea2ab565.poster.avif?t=1653734931\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258020/extras/5ee32287d6f8233060375820ea2ab565.webm?t=1653734931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258020/extras/5ee32287d6f8233060375820ea2ab565.mp4?t=1653734931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258020/extras/0c48a7916d24debe8cb9d7141dfa8ee5.poster.avif?t=1653734931\" width=640 height=320 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258020/extras/0c48a7916d24debe8cb9d7141dfa8ee5.webm?t=1653734931\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1258020/extras/0c48a7916d24debe8cb9d7141dfa8ee5.mp4?t=1653734931\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"http